Tata Steel Says No Decision on Rio Tinto’s Offer for Riversdale

-- B y   A b h a y   S i n g h
-- 
2011-02-23T14:12:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-23/tata-steel-says-no-decision-on-rio-tinto-s-offer-for-riversdale.html
  Tata Steel Ltd . hasn’t taken a
decision on Rio Tinto Group’s offer for Australia’s Riversdale
Mining Ltd., according to an e-mailed statement sent to the
Bombay Stock Exchange today.  Tata reserves the right to make a decision at any time
during Rio Tinto’s offer period, the statement said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Abhay Singh at 
 abhaysingh@bloomberg.net  